                            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white" id="join-heading">Let's build something great together</h2>
                            <p class="text-lg text-white">Ready to take your digital experience to the next level? Whether you're optimizing your site, improving user experience, or building from scratch, let's collaborate.</p>
                            <a class="block w-full rounded-md border border-transparent bg-white px-5 py-3 text-center text-base font-medium text-teal-700 shadow-md hover:bg-gray-200 sm:inline-block sm:w-auto transition" href="{{ url('contact') }}">Get in Touch</a>
